Text: All hot and bothered, muscly sweaty and dark jock straps astink with man juices and you all want to touch one another, posture up on one another, wanting to pointlessly prove yourself by running up and down, up and down and yet it never occurs to you how completely stupid this really is. Fundamentally you must be getting some of that 'Hunter Gatherer' needs met from your ingrained ansestory blood... but if you actually stopped and thought about it.. what a god damn boring waste of time and energy when you could be doing something better to change the fucked up world we live in instead of puffing up your little ego that needs to be the size of Texas. Die all you people. Rot and Die!
